item.title: Career opportunities and YouTube videos
item.description: Hum… I guess it’s been a while since I last blogged. This time however I have something to show off: Till’s and my presentation at CampKDE is on YouTube. And without further ado – enjoy the show. The slides are quite visible in the video but I thought embedding them here wouldn’t hurt. View more presentations from Alexandra Leisse. If you are interested in the rest of the talks, head over to the KDE Promo channel on YouTube and take a look.
